Wargowo  () is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Czarna Dąbrówka, within Bytów County, Pomeranian Voivodeship, in northern Poland. It lies approximately  north of Czarna Dąbrówka,  north of Bytów, and  west of the regional capital Gdańsk.
